data.description: Now is your opportunity to own this spacious 3 Bdrm/ 2 Bath ranch on 1.31 acres! This home has a large living room with a vaulted ceiling that is shared with the oversized kitchen and separate dining area. The home also has a split floor plan with ensuite at the East end of the home and the other bedrooms at the other end. The laundry/mud room leads to the convenient attached garage which houses the mechanicals and a pull down ladder for attic access. In addition, there is a separate 30x40 detached garage that is heated and cooled as well. The center of this garage also has a vaulted ceiling to accommodate a car lift if desired. There is additional overhead storage at the front and rear of this garage. Both the home and garage have new metal roofs that should provide years of worry free protection. The yard extends past the fence, back to the field.
